sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Trainer Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as trainer-controller-manager<br/>(TrainJob Reconciler)
    participant JobSet as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pods<br/>(rank 0)
    participant MPIWorker as MPI Worker Pods<br/>2222/TCP SSH

    Note over User,MPIWorker: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply TrainJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-...-trainjob<br/>TLS (auto-rotated cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: TrainJob created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainJob, TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime spec resolved

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE/PATCH JobSet<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE NetworkPolicy (RHAI)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: UPDATE TrainJob/status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    K8sAPI->>JobSet: Watch event: JobSet created
    JobSet->>K8sAPI: CREATE Jobs & Pods
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: JobSet status update

    Note over User,MPIWorker: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking

    loop Every reconciliation cycle
        Controller->>K8sAPI: LIST Pods (label selector)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list (find rank-0 pod)
        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>No Auth (NetworkPolicy restricted)
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: Prometheus metrics<br/>(training progress)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>(progress data)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    Note over User,MPIWorker: Flow 3: MPI Distributed Training Setup

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE Secret (SSH key pair)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE ConfigMap (MPI hostfile)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created

    Note over TrainingPod,MPIWorker: MPI Communication
    TrainingPod->>MPIWorker: SSH connection<br/>2222/TCP SSH<br/>Auth: RSA key pair
    MPIWorker-->>TrainingPod: Training coordination
